Military Units: Space Force

Military Units: Space Force

The Space Force structure is unique. While it is a separate and distinct branch of the armed services, it is organized under the Department of the Air Force. Its mission is to secure the nation's interests in, from and to space.
title: U.S. Department of Defense

meta_data.DESCRIPTION: The Department of Defense is America's largest government agency. Our mission is to provide the military forces needed to deter war and ensure our nation's security.
